{"id":14881375,"mediaExerciseId":"e498d1df-0bcf-4798-bd98-920f7ef449a1","exerciseName":"4","chapterName":"12","chapterTitle":"Some Lessons From Capital Market History","groupId":612365,"groupTitle":"Minicase Questions","isPremium":true,"sectionName":null,"sectionTitle":null,"pageNumber":419,"solutions":[{"id":6253409,"modifiedOn":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000000","steps":[{"columns":[{"text":"In this problem, we will discuss the implication of volatility in a mutual fund.","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":1},{"columns":[{"text":"Volatility refers to the how much the price of a stock fluctuates. A high volatility means that it may be difficult to predict the future price since the prices fluctuate often and usually in big swings. ","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":2},{"columns":[{"text":"Despite the high volatility, it can still be a good investment since it has higher returns due to its high risk. Depending on the person's risk appetite, they can still invest in this if their strategy fits the risks of this fund. ","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":3},{"columns":[{"text":"Since it has the highest volatility, it takes a lot of skill to manage the funds in order to provide decent returns. This is the reason why they have the highest expenses. This can be a good indicator that the manager of the fund is highly skilled so investing in this mutual fund is a good idea as long as it fits your risk appetite. ","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":4}],"rating":0,"solutionUuid":"b549f220-963c-47c6-8940-9caf4c073354","editorVersion":2,"answeredOn":null,"ratingCount":null,"solutionOrder":null,"totalSteps":4}],"textbook":{"authors":"Bradford D. Jordan, Randolph W